1. 太空不是 “物理环境问题”5 ⽽是 “主体结构断裂问题”
Space Is Not a Physical Environment Problem but a Subjective-Structural Fracture
⼈类以为⽕星移⺠的核⼼难点是-
• 氧⽓
• 能源
• 辐射
• 重⼒
• ⽣态循环
这些当然难5 但都属于 ⼯程问题 bEngineering Problemsc｡
真正⽆法解决的是-
⼈类主观结构在太空中⽆法⾃洽
bSubjective Architecture Cannot Self-Stabilize in Spacec
也就是说-
• ⼈能在太空存活
• 但⽆法在太空保持 “⼈”这个结构的完整运⾏
Space seems difficult because of:
• oxygen
• radiation
• gravity
• ecosystem engineering
But these are solvable engineering problems.
The real unsolved problem:
The human subjective architecture cannot remain coherent in space.
Humans can survive,
