2. ⼈类主观结构依赖 “地球基准线”
Human Subjectivity Requires a “Terrestrial Baseline”
这条是致命的｡
⼈类的主观系统由以下部分组成-
• 时间节律 b昼夜循环c
• ⽣物场域 b⽣物圈反馈c
• 社会氛围 b群体意义流c
• 重⼒参照 b身体位置感c
• 地球背景噪声 b磁场､ 离⼦层､ 环境震荡c
这⼀套是 “⼈类主观结构的运⾏基准线”｡
离开地球后5 ⼈类进⼊-
⽆参照､ ⽆连续性､ ⽆意义流､ ⽆反馈的状态｡
这不是⼼理问题5 是结构问题｡
Human subjectivity depends on:
• circadian rhythm
• biosphere feedback
• social meaning flow
• gravitational reference
• Earth’s ambient electromagnetic & ecological background
This is the baseline of human subjective stability.
Once removed from Earth, humans enter:
a state with no reference, no continuity, no meaning flow, and no stabilizing feedback.
This is structural, not emotional.
