• 情绪倒置
• 主体性漂移
• 价值系统崩解
This is why太空⼼理学数据永远不会公开完整｡
Space removes meaning-generation mechanisms.
Humans enter a meaning vacuum:
• social rhythm disappears
• natural feedback disappears
