• ⽆恰当⻛险
• ⽆⽣态反馈
• ⽆意义熵流
结果是⾃我边界或膨胀､ 或瓦解､ 或僵化､ 或漂移｡
⽆⼀例外｡
Self-boundaries stabilize through:
• small risks
• small rewards
• small failures
• small feedback cycles
This micro-oscillation is Earth-dependent.
Space lacks:
• stochastic variation
• ecological risk
• meaning entropy
• natural rhythm
Result:
Self-boundaries collapse, inflate, drift, or freeze.
All outcomes are dysfunctional.
